        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>Glory to God!</strong></p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="about-me">About Me<a href="https://ece-kits.github.io/Build7Learn/blog/welcome#about-me" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to About Me" title="Direct link to About Me" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<p>I am a passionate technology and VLSI enthusiast with experience in embedded systems and IoT. I've served as a coordinator and volunteer in various workshops conducted in the college and have hands-on experience with platforms like Arduino, ESP32, ESP8266, STM32, 8051, and LoRaWAN. I enjoy exploring new domains and technologies, and I thrive on interacting with people.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="initiative">Initiative<a href="https://ece-kits.github.io/Build7Learn/blog/welcome#initiative" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Initiative" title="Direct link to Initiative" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<p>My inspiration to create this documentation website came from a site built by friends for a Gen AI Bootcamp using Docusaurus. I was part of the KHACKS community at the time, and their project sparked my passion for building one of my own.</p>
